#sidebar GenericCommandsSidebar

= DEL _key1_ _key2_ ... _keyN_ =
_Time complexity: O(1)_

 Remove the specified keys. If a given key does not exist
 no operation is performed for this key. The commnad returns the number of
 keys removed.

== Return value ==

[ReplyTypes Integer reply], specifically:

{{{
an integer greater than 0 if one or more keys were removed
0 if none of the specified key existed
}}}
